# Citation

If you use AI-Mastery-2026 in your research or work, please cite it as follows:

## BibTeX

```bibtex
@software{ai_mastery_2026,
  author = {Kandil7},
  title = {AI-Mastery-2026: The Ultimate AI Engineering Toolkit},
  year = {2026},
  url = {https://github.com/Kandil7/AI-Mastery-2026},
  version = {0.1.0},
  description = {A comprehensive AI Engineer toolkit built from first principles - from mathematical foundations to production deployment},
  keywords = {artificial-intelligence, machine-learning, deep-learning, llm, rag, mlops, education}
}
```

## APA Style

Kandil7 (2026). AI-Mastery-2026: The Ultimate AI Engineering Toolkit (Version 0.1.0) [Computer software]. GitHub. https://github.com/Kandil7/AI-Mastery-2026

## MLA Style

Kandil7. "AI-Mastery-2026: The Ultimate AI Engineering Toolkit." GitHub, 2026, github.com/Kandil7/AI-Mastery-2026.

## Chicago Style

Kandil7. 2026. "AI-Mastery-2026: The Ultimate AI Engineering Toolkit." Version 0.1.0. GitHub. https://github.com/Kandil7/AI-Mastery-2026.

## Harvard Style

Kandil7 (2026) AI-Mastery-2026: The Ultimate AI Engineering Toolkit. Version 0.1.0. Available at: https://github.com/Kandil7/AI-Mastery-2026 (Accessed: DD Month YYYY).

